<h2 class=3D"wp-block-heading">Linear sequences</h2>



<p></p>



<p>Arithmetic sequences are also known as linear sequences. If we represent=
ed an arithmetic sequence on a graph it would form a straight line as it go=
es up (or down) by the same amount each time. Linear means straight.</p>



<p></p>



