009188-2ad9-4a91-916f-c1275121243f">

<p><tnr>-6 + 3 =3D -3</tnr></p>



<p><tnr>-3 + 3 =3D 0</tnr></p>



<p><tnr>0 + 3 =3D 3</tnr> (Note: this is one of the terms given)</p>



<p><tnr>3 + 3 =3D 6</tnr></p>



<p><br>The missing terms are <tnr>-3, 0,</tnr> and <tnr>6</tnr>.</p>

